# LobeHub

> We are a group of e/acc design-engineers, hoping to provide modern design components and tools for AIGC. By adopting the Bootstrapping approach, we aim to provide developers and users with a more open, transparent, and user-friendly product ecosystem. Whether for users or professional developers, LobeHub will be your AI Agent playground. Pioneering the new age of thinking and creating. Built for you, the Super Individual.

## About LobeChat
An open-source, modern-design ChatGPT/LLMs UI/Framework. Supports speech-synthesis, multi-modal, and extensible (function call) plugin system. One-click FREE deployment of your private OpenAI ChatGPT/Claude/Gemini/Groq/Ollama chat application. Features include Chain of Thought reasoning, branching conversations, artifacts support, file upload/knowledge base, multi-model service provider support, local LLM support, visual recognition, TTS & STT voice conversation, text-to-image generation, agent market (GPTs), local/remote database support, multi-user management, PWA support, mobile adaptation, and custom themes.

### Core Features
- **Chain of Thought**: Experience AI reasoning like never before with step-by-step visualization
- **Branching Conversations**: Create multiple conversation branches to explore different paths
- **Artifacts Support**: Interactive artifacts support for enhanced user experience
- **File Upload / Knowledge Base**: File upload and comprehensive knowledge base management with RAG
- **Multi-Model Service Provider Support**: OpenAI, Claude, Gemini, Groq, Ollama, DeepSeek, Qwen, and more
- **Local Large Language Model (LLM) Support**: Run large language models locally with Ollama integration
- **Model Visual Recognition**: Advanced visual recognition capabilities for image understanding
- **TTS & STT Voice Conversation**: Text-to-Speech and Speech-to-Text for seamless voice interactions
- **Text to Image Generation**: Generate images from text with integrated AI models
- **Plugin System (Function Calling)**: Extensible function calling system with 500+ plugins
- **Agent Market (GPTs)**: GPTs-like agent marketplace with pre-built AI agents
- **Support Local / Remote Database**: Flexible database options for local and remote storage
- **Support Multi-User Management**: Enterprise-ready multi-user management and permissions
- **Progressive Web App (PWA)**: Progressive Web App with offline capabilities and native feel
- **Mobile Device Adaptation**: Optimized responsive design for all mobile devices
- **Custom Themes**: Beautiful dark/light themes and customizable UI components
- **Open Source**: MIT licensed, community-driven open source development
- **One-Click Deployment**: Deploy instantly on Vercel, Zeabur, Sealos, Alibaba Cloud, or Docker

LobeHub provides a comprehensive ecosystem for AI applications, pioneering the new age of thinking and creating. Built for you, the Super Individual. Our ecosystem includes:
- **LobeChat**: Modern-design ChatGPT/LLMs UI/Framework with advanced features like Chain of Thought, branching conversations, and multi-modal support
- **MCP Servers**: Model Context Protocol servers for enhanced AI capabilities and integrations
- **Plugin Marketplace**: Extensive collection of AI plugins with function calling capabilities for enhanced functionality
- **Agent Marketplace**: Pre-built AI agents (GPTs) for various use cases and specialized tasks
- **Lobe Icons**: Comprehensive icon library with 3000+ beautifully designed icons for modern applications
- **Resources & Tools**: Brand resources, design guidelines, and development tools for the LobeHub ecosystem
